quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,“Kodi sakudziwa zikadzatulutsidwa za m’manda
  100,10,“Ndikudzasonkhanitsidwa ndi kuonekera poyera zomwe zidali m’mitima
  100,11,“Ndithu tsiku limenelo Mbuye wawo adzawadziwa kwambiri (ndikuwalongosolera zonse zochita zawo)
  101,1,“Kugunda kwa phokoso (la Qiyâma)
  101,2,“Kodi kugunda kwa phokosolo ndi chiyani
  101,3,“Ndichiyani chingakudziwitse za kugunda kwa phokoso (la Qiyâma komwe kudzawakomole anthu)
  101,4,“Limenelo ndi tsiku limene anthu adzakhala ngati agulugufe obalalika
  101,5,“Ndipo mapiri adzakhala ngati ubweya womwazidwa (wongouluka uku ndi uku mumlengalenga)
  101,6,“Tsono amene muyeso wake (wa zinthu zabwino) udzalemere (ndikupepuka zoipa)
  101,7,“Ndiye kuti iye adzakhala mu umoyo wosangalatsa (patsiku la chiweruziro)
  101,8,“Ndipo yemwe muyeso wake (wa zinthu zabwino) udzapepuka (ndi kulemera zoipa)
  101,9,“Ndiye kuti mbuto yake ndi ku Hawiya
  101,10,“Kodi ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za Hawiya
  101,11,“Umenewo ndi Moto woyaka mwa ukali
  102,1,“Kwakutangwanitsani kusonkhanitsa (chuma chambiri ndi ana)
  102,2,“Mpakana mwapita kumanda (mwamwalira ndikukalowa m’manda)
  102,3,“Sichoncho! Mudziwa posachedwapa
  102,4,“Ndiponso sichoncho! Mudziwa posachedwapa
  102,5,"“Sichoncho! mukadakhala mukudziwa, kudziwa kwachitsimikizo (sibwenzi mukutangwanika ndi za mdziko)"
  102,6,“Ndithudi mudzauona Moto
  102,7,“Kenako mudzauona ndithu ndi diso lachitsimikizo
  102,8,“Tsono patsikulo ndithudi mudzafunsidwa za mtendere (omwe munapatsidwa)
  103,1,“Ndikuilumbilira nthawi
  103,2,“Ndithu munthu aliyense ndi wotaika (chifukwa chakugonjetsedwa ndi zilakolako zake)
  103,3,"“Kupatula amene akhulupirira (mwa Allah) ndi kumachita zabwino, ndikumalangizana kutsatira choona ndiponso ndi kumalangizana za kupirira (potsatira malamulo a Allah ndi zina za mdziko)"
  104,1,“Kuonongeka koopsa kudzampeza aliyense wojeda ndi wonyoza anthu polozera (ndi maso kapena kuyankhula ndi lirime)
  104,2,“Yemwe wasonkhanitsa chuma ndikumachiwerengera
  104,3,“Akuganiza kuti chuma chakecho chimkhazika (pa dziko) nthawi yaitali (ndikumteteza ku zimene sakuzifuna)
  104,4,"“Sichoncho! (Asiye maganizo amenewo) ndithudi, akaponyedwa ku Moto woononga (chifukwa cha kuipa kwa zochita zake)"
  104,5,“Ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za Moto woonongawu
  104,6,"“Umenewu ndi Moto wa Allah woyaka (nthawi zonse, woononga chilichonse choponyedwa mmenemo)"
  104,7,“Umene umakwera mpaka ku mtima
  104,8,“Ndithu motowo ukawazinga (ndi kuwatsekera makomo)
  104,9,“Munsanamira za zitalizitali (kotero kuti sakatha kugwedezeka mmenemo kapena kupulumuka)
  105,1,“Kodi sudaone momwe Mbuye wako adawachitira eni njovu
  105,2,“Kodi sadachichite chiwembu chawo kukhala chosokera (chopanda phindu)
  105,3,“Ndipo adawatumizira magulumagulu a mbalame otsatizana. (ndipo adawazungulira mbali zonse)
  105,4,“Zimawagenda ndi miyala ya moto
  105,5,“Choncho adawachita ngati m’mera wodyedwa (ndi nyama ndi kulavulidwa)
  106,1,“Cholinga chakuwachita Maquraish kuti apitirize chizolowezi chawo
  106,2,"“Apitilize chizolowezi chawo choyenda nthawi ya dzinja (kunka ku Yemen) ndi nthawi yachirimwe (kunka ku Sham kukachita malonda, mosatekeseka ndi mopanda mantha)"
  106,3,"“Choncho, amupembedze Mbuye wa Nyumba iyi (Al-Kaaba amene adachititsa kuti athe kuyenda maulendo awiriwo)"
  106,4,"“Yemwe amawadyetsa (nthawi imene Arabu anzawo) ali m’njala, ndipo amawapatsa chitetezo (pomwe anzawo) ali ndi mantha"
  107,1,“Kodi wamuona yemwe akutsutsa za mphoto (ndi chiwerengero cha tsiku lachimaliziro)
  107,2,“Iye ndi yemwe akukankha wamasiye (mwankhanza)
  107,3,“Ndipo salimbikitsa (ena pamodzi ndi iye mwini) kudyetsa osauka
  107,4,“Choncho kuonongeka kuli pa ena mwa opemphera swala (amene ali ndi mbiri izi)
  107,5,“Omwe amachitira mphwayi mapemphero awo
  107,6,“Amenenso (akamachita mapemphero awo) amadzionetsera (kwa anthu mwachipha maso kuti apeze ulemelero ndi kutamandidwa mmitima mwa anthu)
  107,7,"“Ndipo amamana ziwiya (zawo posabwereka anzawo zinthu zofunika pa moyo wa aliyense monga nkhwangwa, mpeni, mtondo ndi zina zotere)"
  108,1,“Ndithu takupatsa zabwino zambiri (zina mwa izo ndi mtsinje wotchedwa Kauthar)
  108,2,"“(Pakuti ndakupatsa zimenezo), pitiriza kupembedza Mbuye wako (moyera mtima) ndipo ipha nsembe yako (chifukwa chakuthokoza Allah pa zimene wakupatsa, monga ulemelero ndikukusankhira zabwino zambiri)"
  108,3,“Ndithu mdani wako ndiye ali wopanda mwawi
  109,1,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki) (s.a.w): E inu anthu osakhulupirira"
  109,2,“Sindipembedza chimene inu mukuchipembedza (kusiya Allah)
  109,3,“Inunso simumpembedza amene ine ndikumpembedza (yemwe ndi Allah)
  109,4,“Ndiponso ine sindidzapembedza chimene inu mwakhala mukuchipembedza (chifukwa inu ndinu ophatikiza Allah ndi zinthu zina)
  109,5,“Ndipo inu simudzampembedza amene ine ndikumpembedza (yemwe ndi Allah)
  109,6,"“Inu muli ndi chipembedzo chanu (chimene mukuchikhulupirira), inenso ndili ndi chipembedzo changa (chimene Allah wandisankhira)"
  110,1,“Chikafika chipulumutso cha Allah ndi kugonjetsa (mzinda wa Makka kwa iwe ndi okutsatira)
  110,2,“Ndikuwaona anthu akulowa m’chipembedzo cha Allah ali magulumagulu
  110,3,"“Pamenepo lemekeza Mbuye wako ndi kumtamanda ndiponso mpemphe chikhululuko, ndipo ndithu Iye ndiwolandira mochuluka kulapa (kwa anthu Ake)"
  111,1,“Aonongeka manja a Abi Lahab (omwe adali kuwagwiritsa ntchito pozunza Asilamu). Nayenso wawonongeka
  111,2,“Chuma chake ndi ulemelero wake (umene adaupeza) sizidamthandize ku chilango cha Allah
  111,3,“Adzalowa ku Moto wa malawi
  111,4,“Nayenso mkazi wake (adzalowa ku Moto) yemwe adali kusenza nkhuni (za minga pomutchera Mtumiki (s.a.w) komanso amanka nadanitsa pakati pa anthu
  111,5,“Mkhosi mwake mdzamangidwa chingwe chopiringidwa bwino cha mlaza (chomlanga nacho)
  112,1,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki (s.a.w), kwa amene akukufunsa mwachipongwe, mbiri za Mulungu wako): “Iye ndi Allah Mmodzi, (alibe mnzake)"
  112,2,“Allah ndi Wokhala ndi zonse Wodaliridwa ndi zolengedwa Zake
  112,3,“Sadabale (mwana) ndiponso sadaberekedwe
  112,4,“Ndiponso palibe aliyense wofanana ndi Iye.”
  113,1,"“Nena: “Ndikudzitchinjiriza ndi Mbuye wam’bandakucha"
  113,2,“Kuchokera ku zoipa zimene Iye adazilenga
  113,3,“Ndi ku zoipa za usiku pamene mdima ukulowa mwa mphamvu
  113,4,“Ndi ku zoipa za afiti omwe amauzira mu mfundo
  113,5,“Ndiponso ku zoipa za wansanje pamene akuchita nsanje.”
  114,1,"“Nena: “Ndikudzitchinjiriza ndi Mbuye (Mleri) wa anthu (Yemwe akulinganiza zinthu zawo)"
  114,2,“Mfumu ya anthu ( Imene iri ndi mphamvu yochita chirichonse pa iwo)
  114,3,“Wopembedzedwa wa anthu
  114,4,“Kuzoipa za mnong’onezi (yemwe amathira unong’onezi wake m’mitimaya anthu) yemwenso amabisala (posiya unong’onezi wake ngati mwini mtimawo atankumbukira Allah)
  114,5,“Yemwe amanong’oneza mzifuwa za anthu
  114,6,“Wochokera m’ziwanda ndi mwa anthu.”